test_name: If day to day experience is more than once a year, at least one main reason for the experience must be checked
short_desc: At least one of the following variables must be equal to 1: EXPANCEST,EXPGENDER, EXPRACE, EXPAGE, EXPRELIG, EXPHEIGHT, EXPWEIGHT, EXPAPPEAR, EXPSEXORN, EXPEDUCINC, EXPDISAB, EXPSKIN, EXPNOANS
full_desc: At least one of the following variables must be equal to 1: Q37a1. EXPANCEST, Q37a2. EXPGENDER, Q37a3. EXPRACE, Q37a4. EXPAGE, Q37a5. EXPRELIG, Q37a6. EXPHEIGHT, Q37a7. EXPWEIGHT, Q37a8. EXPAPPEAR, Q37a9. EXPSEXORN, Q37a10. EXPEDUCINC, Q37a11. EXPDISAB, Q37a12. EXPSKIN, Q37a13. EXPOTHER, Q37a14. EXPNOTAPP, Q37a15. EXPNOANS
test_logic: IF EXPDAY in (1,2,3,4) and (EXPANCEST ne 1 and EXPGENDER ne 1 and EXPRACE ne 1 and EXPAGE ne 1 and EXPRELIG ne 1 and EXPHEIGHT ne 1 and  EXPWEIGHT ne 1 and EXPAPPEAR ne 1 and EXPSEXORN ne 1 and EXPEDUCINC ne 1 and EXPDISAB ne 1 and EXPSKIN ne 1 and EXPOTHER ne 1 and EXPNOTAPP ne 1 and EXPNOANS ne 1)
comp_vars:
EXPANCEST,
EXPGENDER,
EXPRACE,
EXPAGE,
EXPRELIG,
EXPHEIGHT,
EXPWEIGHT,
EXPAPPEAR,
EXPSEXORN,
EXPEDUCINC,
EXPDISAB,
EXPSKIN,
EXPOTHER,
EXPNOTAPP
EXPNOANS
